22:28.597 --> 22:30.640
DUE TO THE SUDDEN ONSET
OF ADOLESCENCE.

22:30.724 --> 22:33.685
- [wailing]

22:33.769 --> 22:35.479
- TATE!

22:37.022 --> 22:41.943
♪ ANY DAY NOW ♪

22:42.027 --> 22:44.988
♪ THEY'RE GONNA TELL ME
I'M TOO OLD ♪

22:45.072 --> 22:50.077
♪ SO I BETTER WRITE
ANOTHER HIT ♪

